He didn't dispatch troops from
Zhennan Pass to accompany him?

00:21:59.240 --> 00:21:59.990
No.

00:22:00.270 --> 00:22:01.560
I heard that the escorts

00:22:01.560 --> 00:22:02.310
are all from

